    <item>
      <title>Làm chủ JavaScript DOM Manipulation</title>
      <link>http://example.org/posts/js-dom/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 17:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://example.org/posts/js-dom/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;dom-là-gì&#34;&gt;DOM là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;DOM (Document Object Model) là cách trình duyệt biểu diễn trang HTML của bạn dưới dạng một cây (tree) các đối tượng. JavaScript thông qua DOM để thay đổi nội dung, cấu trúc và kiểu dáng của trang web một cách động.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-chọn-phần-tử-selecting-elements&#34;&gt;1. Chọn phần tử (Selecting Elements)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Quên &lt;code&gt;getElementById&lt;/code&gt; hay &lt;code&gt;getElementsByClassName&lt;/code&gt; đi nếu bạn muốn code hiện đại. Hãy dùng bộ đôi quyền lực:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;document.querySelector(&#39;selector&#39;)&lt;/code&gt;: Chọn phần tử đầu tiên khớp với CSS selector.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;document.querySelectorAll(&#39;selector&#39;)&lt;/code&gt;: Chọn TẤT CẢ phần tử khớp (trả về NodeList).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;querySelector&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;#main-title&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;buttons&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;querySelectorAll&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.btn-click&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-thay-đổi-nội-dung-và-style&#34;&gt;2. Thay đổi nội dung và Style&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;querySelector&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.box&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Đổi nội dung&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;textContent&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Nội dung mới&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// An toàn hơn innerHTML&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// box.innerHTML = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Đậm&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;#34;; // Cẩn thận XSS attack&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Đổi Style trực tiếp&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;style&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;backgroundColor&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;red&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;style&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;fontSize&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;20px&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Thêm/Xóa Class (Khuyên dùng thay vì sửa style trực tiếp)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;classList&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;active&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;classList&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;remove&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;hidden&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;classList&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;toggle&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;dark-mode&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-lắng-nghe-sự-kiện-event-listeners&#34;&gt;3. Lắng nghe sự kiện (Event Listeners)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Đừng bao giờ dùng &lt;code&gt;onclick=&amp;quot;...&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt; trong HTML. Hãy tách biệt logic ra khỏi giao diện bằng &lt;code&gt;addEventListener&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
